  "schedule_type": "string (daily|weekly|monthly|custom)",
  "time_of_day": "string (HH:MM format OR 'multiple')",
  "times": "array (optional - required when time_of_day='multiple')",

  "day_of_month": "number (optional for monthly)",
  "timezone": "string (default: user_timezone)"
}
